<article id="post-67874" class="post-67874 post type-post status-publish format-standard has-post-thumbnail hentry category-books category-latest-releases tag-monthly-releases tag-publisher-agnostic">

	<header class="entry-header">
		<!--<div class="entry-cats">
					</div>< end .entry-cats -->

		<h1 class="entry-title">The best books out in August</h1>
		<div class="entry-author">
			
            August 1, 2019

		</div><!-- end .entry-author -->

	</header><!-- end .entry-header -->

	
			<div class="entry-thumbnail">
			<!-- <a href="" title="">-->
			<img width="1020" height="400" src="https://3hpx593011wh163cdd3z657b-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/The-best-books-out-in-August-2019v2.jpg" class="attachment-zuki-fullwidth size-zuki-fullwidth wp-post-image jetpack-lazy-image" alt="best books out in august 2019" data-attachment-id="67968" data-permalink="https://www.deadgoodbooks.co.uk/best-books-out-in-august-2019/the-best-books-out-in-august-2019v2/" data-orig-file="https://www.deadgoodbooks.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/The-best-books-out-in-August-2019v2.jpg" data-orig-size="1020,400" data-comments-opened="0" data-image-meta="{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}" data-image-title="The-best-books-out-in-August-2019v2" data-image-description="" data-medium-file="https://www.deadgoodbooks.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/The-best-books-out-in-August-2019v2-300x118.jpg" data-large-file="https://www.deadgoodbooks.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/The-best-books-out-in-August-2019v2.jpg" data-lazy-srcset="https://3hpx593011wh163cdd3z657b-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/The-best-books-out-in-August-2019v2.jpg 1020w, https://3hpx593011wh163cdd3z657b-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/The-best-books-out-in-August-2019v2-300x118.jpg 300w, https://3hpx593011wh163cdd3z657b-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/The-best-books-out-in-August-2019v2-768x301.jpg 768w" data-lazy-sizes="(max-width: 1020px) 100vw, 1020px" data-lazy-src="https://3hpx593011wh163cdd3z657b-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/The-best-books-out-in-August-2019v2.jpg?is-pending-load=1" srcset="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAIBRAA7" />		  <!--</a> -->
		</div><!-- end .entry-thumbnail -->

        
	
	<div class="entry-content">

		<div class="article-body">


			<p>It&#8217;s safe to say Julyâ€™s weather was a little unpredictable &#8211; and knowing the great British summer, August&#8217;s is likely to be just as unreliable. But one thing is for certain: there are loads of brilliant new books to keep us occupied, come rain or shine. Or hail, thunder, lightning&#8230;</p>
<p>With exciting new releases from the likes of Harlan Coben, Val McDermid and Ruth Ware, whether you like your crime dark and psychological or prefer escaping with an atmospheric detective novel, this month has something for you.</p>
<p>The weather might not know what it&#8217;s up to, but we sure know what we&#8217;ll be doing: lots and lots of reading. Here&#8217;s our pick of the best books out in August. </p>
<h2>The best books out in August 2019:</h2>
<div class="row3 cover-row">
<div class="image-wrapper"><a href="https://www.amazon.co.uk/Family-Upstairs-Lisa-Jewell/dp/1780899203/?tag=prhmarketing10454-21" rel="noopener" target="_blank"><img data-attachment-id="67421" data-permalink="https://www.deadgoodbooks.co.uk/extract-the-family-upstairs-by-lisa-jewell/the-family-upstairs/" data-orig-file="https://www.deadgoodbooks.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/The-Family-Upstairs.jpg" data-orig-size="1840,2835" data-comments-opened="0" data-image-meta="{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}" data-image-title="The Family Upstairs" data-image-description data-medium-file="https://www.deadgoodbooks.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/The-Family-Upstairs-195x300.jpg" data-large-file="https://www.deadgoodbooks.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/The-Family-Upstairs-665x1024.jpg" src="https://3hpx593011wh163cdd3z657b-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/The-Family-Upstairs.jpg" alt="best books out in august 2019" class="alignleft size-medium wp-image-67421 jetpack-lazy-image" data-lazy-srcset="https://3hpx593011wh163cdd3z657b-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/The-Family-Upstairs.jpg 1840w, https://3hpx593011wh163cdd3z657b-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/The-Family-Upstairs-195x300.jpg 195w, https://3hpx593011wh163cdd3z657b-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/The-Family-Upstairs-768x1183.jpg 768w, https://3hpx593011wh163cdd3z657b-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/The-Family-Upstairs-665x1024.jpg 665w, https://3hpx593011wh163cdd3z657b-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/The-Family-Upstairs-220x340.jpg 220w" data-lazy-size